                "text": "<p>We use personal information to:</p><ul><li>Process and fulfill orders</li><li>Handle payments, shipping, returns, and exchanges</li><li>Provide order confirmations and support updates</li><li>Improve and personalize the customer experience</li><li>Send marketing communications (if you’ve opted in)</li><li>Display relevant promotions and ads across platforms</li><li>Detect, investigate, or prevent fraudulent activity</li><li>Comply with legal obligations and maintain records</li></ul><p>You can unsubscribe from marketing emails at any time using the link in any email we send.</p>",
