            "text_LQNHtV": {
              "type": "text",
              "name": "t:names.text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<p>We use cookies and related technologies to:</p><ul><li>Operate our store and remember your preferences</li><li>Analyze website traffic and performance</li><li>Measure marketing effectiveness</li><li>Provide personalized advertising experiences</li></ul><p><strong>Google Analytics 4 & Google Tag Manager</strong></p><p>We use Google Analytics 4 (GA4) and Google Tag Manager to analyze site usage and visitor behavior.</p><p>Google may collect data such as your IP address, device information, and on-site actions to help us improve the Site.</p><p>You can learn more about how Google uses data here: <a href=\"https://policies.google.com/technologies/partner-sites\">https://policies.google.com/technologies/partner-sites</a>. To opt out of Google Analytics, install the browser add-on at <a href=\"https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout\">https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout</a>.</p><p><strong>Klaviyo</strong></p><p></p><p>We use Klaviyo to send marketing emails and SMS communications and to analyze engagement (opens, clicks, purchases).Klaviyo may use cookies or tracking pixels to personalize content and measure performance.Learn more:<a href=\"https://www.klaviyo.com/legal/privacy\">https://www.klaviyo.com/legal/privacy</a>.</p><p><strong>Okendo </strong></p><p>We use Okendo to collect and display customer reviews and feedback. When you submit a review, your name, rating, and comments may be publicly visible.Learn more:<a href=\"https://www.okendo.io/privacy-policy\">https://www.okendo.io/privacy-policy</a>.You can disable cookies in your browser settings, but some features may not function properly if cookies are turned off.</p>",
                "width": "fit-content",
                "max_width": "none",
                "alignment": "left",
