            "text_9aABdH": {
              "type": "text",
              "name": "t:names.text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<p>We share personal information with trusted partners only when necessary to operate our business, such as:</p><ul><li>Shopify (our ecommerce platform provider)</li><li>Payment processors for secure transactions</li><li>Shipping and logistics providers</li><li>Analytics and advertising partners (Google, Meta, Klaviyo)</li><li>Review tools (Okendo)</li><li>IT and cloud service providers for data storage and support</li></ul><p><strong>We do not sell personal information.</strong></p><p>Some partners may use cookies for cross-site advertising that qualifies as “sharing” under certain laws; you may opt out of targeted ads via your ad-platform settings (e.g., Google Ads, Facebook Ads).</p>",
